data.description:
Welcome home to this charming 4 bedroom and 2 ½ bathroom home nestled in the quaint neighborhood of Sandstone. This delightful property offers a second chance for those seeking the perfect blend of Southern comfort and modern living. With a classic exterior and a tastefully updated interior, this residence beckons you with its welcoming atmosphere.
The home features ample space for both relaxation and entertainment. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances and stylish finishes. The floor plan seamlessly connects the living and dining areas, creating an ideal space for gatherings and family moments.
Step outside to discover a spacious backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and enjoying the mild Southern climate. The property's landscaping adds a touch of natural beauty, creating a serene retreat. Additionally, the back-on-market status presents a unique opportunity for prospective buyers to make this house their own and turn it into a personalized haven. Be sure to ask about the Assumable Loan availability. 
Located in the charming town of Aiken, this home offers convenient access to local amenities, parks, and restaurants. Don't miss the chance to own a home in Aiken's rich history and Southern hospitality. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities that await in this gem.
